comment: Johnson (MIA) and Biyombo (TOR) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.

Whiteside (MIA) firms up as he sets the screen on Joseph (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.

Contact initiated by Dragic (MIA) does not dislodge Lowry (TOR).
